{"lastModified":1772795172559,"uri":"c::9974682422::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Mykonos, Greece\n\nThe new T41 Power Cat starts a new concept of Power Cat division inside Tesoro Yachts range in addition to the walkaround models.\n\nThis new model has been created to offer an extremely comfortable spaces to enjoy on 41 feet boat the same features and options you can find on a bigger yachts.\n\nYou will be able to make medium and large range cruises in maximum comfort with extremely large space at your disposal where you can enjoy while navigation is taking place like on a big yacht is possible to be done.\n\nTwo independent gullwing doors give you the entrance to an independent twin cabins with its own WC and shower area each one; with an elegant, luxury and modern character ideally created for the owner who wants to experience the boat as a villa or private island on the sea.\nSpaces and volumes perfectly designed to optimize each corner of the boat, from the living area to the accommodation spaces.\n\nFor the exteriors, large sundecks and lounge areas on the aft and foredeck will be the perfect terraces to enjoy a privileged contact with the sea.","blueprint":{"name":"TESORO 41 POWER CAT","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098::assets::c4df1ee0-a80e-11ef-ad47-51c68c92e1cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098::assets::c4dc86d0-a80e-11ef-ad45-51c68c92e1cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098::assets::c4d6e180-a80e-11ef-ad43-51c68c92e1cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098::assets::c4d84110-a80e-11ef-ad43-51c68c92e1cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::867ee8c0-a80d-11ef-a750-ff0a255dd098::assets::1166f2b0-a80f-11ef-9820-df9512edf705/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel: